divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing on my porch last night at about 9 and was taking of the full moon. I took 3pics in a row when I came back inside and looked at the pics is when I saw a strange looking object in the 1st pic and not the other two. Thought it is very odd. And would like to get your opinion on it. And no it is not Photoshop by any means. I am sending all 3 pics
trends: There have been no other sightings in same as above
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: i was taking a pic of the full moon last night. took 3pics and the object only appered in the 1st. one
